{"tid":2137154,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無最近分手既巴打 入一入黎","createTime":"2020-08-02T16:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T16:49:58.000Z","uid":180204,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7eafcc183e00d1224826b787d470d6f0b044d5a0","tid":2137154,"uid":180204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:31:16.000Z","msg":"喂廢柴<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解你俾人飛呀<br />\n<br />\n因為你窮 柒 無料丫嘛<br />\n<br />\n一個又窮又柒又廢既人喊晒口叫你唔好分手 你都想一腳踢開佢 叫佢收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做男人 好簡單姐<br />\n<br />\n你係靚仔就玩晒既<br />\n<br />\n唔靚仔咪問下自己有無家底 有錢就玩撚晒<br />\n<br />\n咁乜都無<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚心你就增值下自己 做番個男人<br />\n<br />\n你無野lead到條女 咁就仆街啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現實就係咁<br />\n十分你俾自己幾多分？你又評你條女幾分？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會建議你增值到自己起碼優越個條女至少兩分<br />\n<br />\n咁就長拍長有啦"},{"pid":"162e7c836986cb60f79c009a641f315db8ca6475","tid":2137154,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:36:27.000Z","msg":"所以我開聲飛佢先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樣都係咁sad"},{"pid":"64a3a86b8b82203ef0ea9f6da58f32d748f287fa","tid":2137154,"uid":180204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162e7c836986cb60f79c009a641f315db8ca6475","tid":2137154,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:36:27.000Z","msg":"所以我開聲飛佢先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一樣都係咁sad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:49:58.000Z","msg":"唔驚，遲早佢飛你<br />\n<br />\n今日be a better man<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}